Package: obmodeling
Type: Package
Title: Modeling, Analysis, and Graphics of Limit Order Book Data
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: c(
      person("Jeffrey", "Mazar", email = "jeffrey.mazar@gmail.com", role = c("cre", "aut"))
      , person("Brian", "Peterson", email = "brian@braverock.com",role = c("aut"))
    )
Description: 
    The obmodeling package is designed to allow for modeling of order book
    features and dynamics based on L1 and L2 data.  It includes analytical
    methods and graphics drawns from the microstructure literature and aims
    to be useful both for academics and working professionals.
Depends: R (>= 3.3.0)
Imports: xts
License: GPL-2
LazyData: true
